 selected sections. Processing time depends on your starting point and desired lift. The appointment finishes with a custom toner, conditioning treatment, and style. Plan for a longer appointment — beautiful blonde takes patience."}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoBlock","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoItem","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoLabel","children":"Pricing"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoValue","children":"Starting at $200"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoDivider"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoItem","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoLabel","children":"Duration"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoValue","children":"2 hr 30 min+"}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__cta","children":["$","a",null,{"href":"/book","className":"Button-module__zVQJKW__button Button-module__zVQJKW__primary Button-module__zVQJKW__fullWidth","children":"Book This Service"}]}],["$","aside",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__ashleyNote","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__noteLabel","children":"A note from Ashley"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__noteText","children":"I am very protective of my blondes. Lived-in placement is about restraint — knowing where not to put highlights is just as important as knowing where to put them. I want your blonde to look effortless, not overdone."}]]}]]}]}],[["$","link","0",{"rel":"stylesheet","href":"/_next/static/chunks/0~ww8ls-m-185.css","precedence":"next"}],["$","link","1",{"rel":"stylesheet","href":"/_next/static/chunks/0u4.swdsoosqq.css","precedence":"next"}],["$","script","script-0",{"src":"/_next/static/chunks/17atglk0iug8t.js","async":true}]],["$","$L3",null,{"children":["$","$4",null,{"name":"Next.MetadataOutlet","children":"$@5"}]}]]}]